headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Collect Extra Dividends for Your Executive Business Prowess
content:
Executives and Gunrunners sitting on surplus stock can offload their goods at a premium this week â€“ both Special Cargo and Gunrunning Sell Missions are paying out an extra 50% GTA$ and RP for successful deliveries.

To launch the Special Cargo Missions, players must first acquire a CEO office and then purchase Special Cargo Warehouse from their office PC through SecuroServ.
